# Project Overview

This is a note-taking application that combines several productivity methodologies:

- **Zettelkasten**: A system of interconnected atomic notes with bidirectional linking
- **Org-style syntax**: Structured document format with hierarchical organization
- **GTD (Getting Things Done)**: Task management system for action items
- **Journal functionality**: Chronological recording of thoughts and events
- **Meeting notes system**: Specialized note-taking for meetings

## Core Requirements

- Zero-cost deployment and operation
- PostgreSQL database with Ecto for data persistence
- Deployment on fly.io (free tier)
- Built with Elixir/Phoenix
